 id=47920787&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;积分：352&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; # 评论: 130&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 12:35:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://github.com/dirac-run/dirac</guid></item><item><title>中国阻止 Meta 收购人工智能初创公司 Manus</title><link>https://www.cnbc.com/2026/04/27/meta-manus-china-blocks-acquisition-ai-startup.html</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-blocks-foreign-acquisition-ai-startup-manus-2026-04-27/" rel="nofollow"&gt;https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-blocks-fore...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/cj0v0gr2yz7o" rel="nofollow"&gt;https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/cj0v0gr2yz7o&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr /&gt;&lt;p&gt;评论网址： &lt;a href="https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=47920315"&gt;https://news.ycombinator.com/item?&lt;/a&gt; id=47920315&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;积分：377&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; # 评论：275&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 11:43:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.cnbc.com/2026/04/27/meta-manus-china-blocks-acquisition-ai-startup.html</guid></item><item><title>盯着墙壁看的男人</title><link>https://www.alexselimov.com/posts/men_who_stare_at_walls/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;文章网址： &lt;a href="https://www.alexselimov.com/posts/men_who_stare_at_walls/"&gt;https://www.alexselimov.com/posts/men_who_stare_at_walls/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;评论网址： &lt;a href="https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=47920074"&gt;https://news.ycombinator.com/item?&lt;/a&gt; id=47920074&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;积分：638&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; # 评论：291&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 11:08:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.alexselimov.com/posts/men_who_stare_at_walls/</guid></item><item><title>Pgbackrest 不再维护</title><link>https://github.com/pgbackrest/pgbackrest</link><description>&lt;p&gt;文章网址： &lt;a href="https://github.com/pgbackrest/pgbackrest"&gt;https://github.com/pgbackrest/pgbackrest&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt